           comment = "Apache OpenDAL Rust crate"),
    person("Hiroaki", "Yutani", role = "cph",
           comment = "savvy R/Rust interface inspiration and dependency")
    )
Description: Provides a byte-oriented abstract filesystem interface for R backed
    by the Rust crate of 'Apache OpenDAL' <https://opendal.apache.org/>. The
    package is designed around filesystem primitives, asynchronous Aio-like
    operations inspired by
    'nanonext', pluggable raw-vector serializers, and a native C API for direct
    async byte access by other R packages.
